%% Diagram: Direct-to-storage two-phase upload (presigned URL)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant A as App API
    participant S as Object store

    C->>A: POST /uploads
    A->>A: sign URL (short TTL)
    A-->>C: upload_url, upload_id

    Note over C,S: Bytes flow direct,\nbypassing API
    loop per chunk
        C->>S: PUT bytes
        S-->>C: 2xx + ETag
    end

    C->>A: complete(upload_id)
    A->>S: verify object
    S-->>A: 200 OK
    A-->>C: 201 Created
